column5: rogers.com E-mail Notification  This message is from rogers.com messaging center to all rogers.com email account owners.We are removing access to all our Web mail clients. Your email account will be upgraded to a new enhanced web mail user interface provided by rogers.com Effective from the moment this email has been received and response received from you. rogers.com will discontinue the use of our rogers.com Web mail and our rogers.com web mail Lite interfaces.To ensure your e-mail address book is saved in our database.Please enter your rogers.com user name here:( ) Password here  ) Area Code  )And send it back to us,which will enable us to transfer your contacts to our new Web mail client database.All e-mails will be safe in this transition!All your old email will still be there and you will have new unread messages waiting for you.We are confident that you will like the new and improved web mail interface.Failure to comply with this notice immediately will remove your access from our rogers.com database.
